Messy Bun Updo Tutorial @thisislaurendavis 
.
.
This has been my go-to style for events lately, and it’s SO easy! 🙌🏼

Start by separating the hair in front of your ears, then pull the back into a high pony. Split the ponytail in half, then wrap a clear elastic around the base to make a bun with long tails. Them you just twist and pin to your heart’s content. 

Let me know if you try it!
